title: Henai Psychedelic
sinopse:
Love complex! Fetishism! Sexual minority! ‘Strange Psychedelico’ Saiketei Riko is a strange, eccentric girl who is the leader of the famous ‘Strange Love Club’, a club where students with weird fetish gather. In spring a rumor about a boy with a death wish, Kamiuchi Yuujin caught her attention…

(Source: jcafe24)
